# ============================================================================
# RUN-V2-VwapBounce - VWAP Bounce Strategy
# ============================================================================
#
# CHART ANALYSIS (Live Data):
# - Current: ~$20.70 | VWAP: ~$20.55 | EMA(9): ~$20.65
# - ADX: 7.34 (VERY WEAK - ranging market)
# - Status: Price testing VWAP support
# - Range: $20.40 - $21.00 consolidation
#
# STRATEGY:
# Buy on VWAP test and bounce. Look for higher lows forming as
# confirmation of buyers stepping in at VWAP support.
#
# ╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
# ║  VWAP BOUNCE PATTERN                                                      ║
# ║                                                                           ║
# ║  $21.00 ─────────────────────────────────────────                        ║
# ║                    /\              /\                                     ║
# ║             /\    /  \    /\      /  \                                   ║
# ║  VWAP ═════/══\══/════\══/══\════/════\═══════                           ║
# ║           /    \/      \/    \__/                                        ║
